; Coverage test for textual_directives.cc lines 291-292, 886-889
; apply year directive and top-level year directive

apply year 2023

2023/06/01 Before year change
    Expenses:Food            $10.00
    Assets:Cash

end apply year

year 2024

01/15 After year directive
    Expenses:Food            $20.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg
23-Jun-01 Before year change    Expenses:Food                $10.00       $10.00
                                Assets:Cash                 $-10.00            0
24-Jan-15 After year directive  Expenses:Food                $20.00       $20.00
                                Assets:Cash                 $-20.00            0
end test
